	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />These times I have been thinking about the better known alternative to Windows, that is especially popular among harcore informaticians.
<br />Does anyone here have it ? Has anyone had a (good or bad) experience (trying) switching from Windows to Linux ? Is a Linux platform more or less suitable for homebrew developpement and emulation or does it make no difference ? Does it exists DOS emulators that allows one to run DOS programms under Linux (or even better, Windows emulator) ?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

